{
  "stem": "22660.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were just sort of close together and opened up and there were just-- just draperies in between where my brother and I slept and the people that rented it to us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- I guess they were also from Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Oh, I don't know really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they were poor people that-- that rented rooms to-- to earn some money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was very primitive, very, very primitive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother had to cook on a Primus it was called, some kind of a concoction of whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you know, she wasn't used to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was so hard for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was difficult times for my parents, very difficult times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The only thing was that ultimately we did rent an apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then our lift-- all our furniture was still in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But since my grandparents were still there, they were able to pack it for us and send it to us to Montevideo, which was very fortunate, so that we had our furniture and pictures and things.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My-- my grandmother saw to it that it was all packed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We got it there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I still remember our-- the huge piano that was lifted up to get through the window up there on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it didn't get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, it crashed into 10,000 pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We never again had a piano in our lives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And it was-- it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We then rented rooms to other German Jewish people and made money that way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was a struggle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was a struggle probably for two or three years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then we already got into a nicer apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But first we had to get my grandmother out yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
